# AGENTS.md

## How to invoke agents

### VS Code (GitHub Copilot Chat)
Type `@<agentname>` in Copilot Chat — e.g. `@__COORDINATOR_ROLE__ route this task`.
Or open the agent picker dropdown and select from the list.

### Claude Code
Claude Code reads `CLAUDE.md` automatically at session start. The `## Agent Context` section summarises the roster and handoffs. Read `AGENTS.md` for full details.

### Cursor
Agents apply via globs — open a file matching the agent's glob pattern and it activates.

### Codex
Agents are registered in `agents/openai.yaml`. The skill activates on `$__SKILL_NAME__` prefix.

